## @Mugamba669
### Audio Visualiser with shaders, AudioApi and THREE.js

## Technologies used
- THREE.js
- WebGL
- Web Audio API
- WebGL Shaders
- HTML5 Canvas
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Vite

